stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> PENDING_MESSAGE: Redis 预占成功
    PENDING_MESSAGE --> MESSAGE_SENT: MQ ACK
    PENDING_MESSAGE --> MESSAGE_SENT: 扫描补发成功

    MESSAGE_SENT --> ORDER_CREATED: PostgreSQL 订单事务成功
    MESSAGE_SENT --> RELEASE_PENDING: 最终拒绝或订单失败
    PENDING_MESSAGE --> RELEASE_PENDING: 确认无法继续发送

    RELEASE_PENDING --> RELEASED: Redis 补偿成功
    RELEASE_PENDING --> MANUAL_REVIEW: 多次补偿失败

    MESSAGE_SENT --> MANUAL_REVIEW: 长期状态未知
    PENDING_MESSAGE --> MANUAL_REVIEW: 超过恢复窗口
